result.text:
By its very principle, a FishEye lens introduces a distortion that strongly curves all straight lines that do not pass through the center. In the photo below, taken from the video, there is no FishEye lens on this camera because, as can be seen without a doubt, no straight line not passing through the center is curved.

Have a good day.
